			
1. Entered the  two numbers and find the range between two numbers?
Ans:- The Code For The Above Program:-
<html>
<body style="background-color:gray;">
<h2> Range Between the number and the sum</h2>

<?php
$a=1;
$b=30;

echo "Enter The First Number:".$a."</br>";

echo "Enter The Second Number:".$b."</br>";
$ans=0;
for($a=1;$a<=30;$a++)
{
    $ans=$ans+$a;
}
echo "Answer between the number is:-".$ans;
 ?>
</body>
</html>

The OutPut:-

 


2. Design a php script to demonstrate all php string function in it?
Ans:- The Code For The Above Program:-

<html>
<body style="background-color:pink;">
<h2> String Function</h2>
<?php

      $str = "Rakesh";
      
      echo "<b>String Length is : </b>". strlen ("Welcome To Info-sis")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>String is : </b>". strstr  ("Welcome To Info-sis","Info-sis")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>String Position is : </b>". strpos  ("Welcome To Info-sis","Info-sis")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>String change is : </b>". str_replace ("World","RKU ","Hello World ")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>Return part of a string : </b>".substr ("RK University","6")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>Remove character from both side :</b>".trim ($str,"Rity")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>Remove character from right side : </b>". rtrim ($str,"University")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>Remove character from left side : </b>".ltrim ($str,"RK")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>String in Lower case : </b>". strtolower ("Welcome To RKU")."<br><br>";
      
      echo "<b>String in Upper case : </b>". strtoupper ("RK University")."<br><br>";    
      
      echo "<b>String all word first character is in Upper case : </b>".ucwords ("rk university");
      
      
?>
</body>
</html>

The Output:-
 





